NOTES:: Columns B and C here are for reference only, so the data capturer can link NAPPI code in this sheet easier to BASE sheet
Pricing is a variable value, and hence goes into the RANKING file. No pricing data in BASE file.
RANKING is te order in which the products will be displayed. HIGHEST ranking for
NAPPI_CODE is the key linking BASE sheet with RANKING sheet.
If PROMOTION_FROM and PROMOTION_TO is blank, REGULAR_PRICE will be used, and RANKING will not be in effect.
PRICE values are EXCLUSIVE OF VAT
If PROMOTION_FROM and PROMOTION_TO is NOT blank, the PROMOTION_PRICE will be used.Highest RANKING gets 1st spot.
If more than one product with a ranking exists, and FIRST spot was already awarded, those with rankings are highest to lowest, then
only will items without any ranking be displayed.
All PRICE columns MUST be in format of RANDS.CENTS, with PERIOD as R/c separator, Spaces will be trimmed out, as per
lines 29 - 32, for example, to become 27738.26. DO NOT use COMMAS in price colums at all.
PLEASE DELETE ALL COLUMNS FROM I ONWARDS BEFORE IMPORTING.
